replaceExistingAssociation.description: Boolean whether the Gateway Attachment should remove any current Route Table association before associating with the specified Route Table. Default value: `false`. This argument is intended for use with EC2 Transit Gateways shared into the current account, otherwise the `transit_gateway_default_route_table_association` argument of the `aws.ec2transitgateway.VpcAttachment` resource should be used.
